  "sector": "Industrials",
  "industry": "Building Products & Equipment",
  "currency": "CNY",
  "website": "https://www.bnbm.com.cn",
  "description": "Beijing New Building Materials Public Limited Company, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells building materials in China. It operates through Light Building Material, Water-Proof Building Material, and Coatings and Building Material divisions. The company offers gypsum board products, such as fire-resistant, water-resistant, formaldehyde-removal, anti-cracking and anti-sagging, perforated, and phase-change gypsum boards; multifunctional, mineral wool, and fiber cement boards; light steel and T-grid studs; internal and exterior paintings; joint compound gypsum, binders, leveling putty, putty powder, and self-leveling gypsum; insulating materials, such as rock wool board and felt, and granulated wool; waterproof materials; flooring products, including commercial heterogeneous vinyl sheets, special and sports flooring, vinyl planks, homogeneous vinyl flooring, and ninyl composition tiles; and ceiling and partition accessories, as well as special tools, keels, and architectural and industrial coatings. It also provides interior wall systems, such as ordinary partition, fire- and water-resistant, sound absorption, CH stud shaft, and veneer wall systems; standard, functional, and decorative ceiling systems; and exterior wall systems. In addition, the company engages in the manufacturing and sale of mortar, architectural hardware, and paint; import and export of building materials; wastewater treatment; environmental protection technology consulting; waterproofing construction; and new material technology promotion services. Its products are used in public buildings, home decorations, renovation, subway tunnels, and industrial buildings. Beijing New Building Materials Public Limited Company was founded in 1979 and is based in Beijing, China.",
